{"tid":1022675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美120億「兆彩」頭獎無人領　兩月後作廢","createTime":"2019-02-15T07:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T11:37:53.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3d967bdd66bfec4bd83256f475653a5a036fd8fa","tid":1022675,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美120億「兆彩」頭獎無人領　兩月後作廢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國「兆彩」（Mega Millions）彩票去年10月有一注中，可獲15.37億美元（約120億港元）獎金，但得獎者至今仍未現身，若再無人領獎，頭獎將在兩個月後作廢。<br />\n<br />\n這張頭獎彩票去年10月在南卡羅來納州辛普森維爾（Simpsonville）售出，但至今仍無人領獎。當地註冊會計師史蒂文森（David Stevenson）表示，「我理解等到2019年可能會有稅收方面的好處，但現在我看不到再等待的必要。老實說，我認為彩票已經丟失。」<br />\n<br />\n中獎者可以選擇一次過取得8.78億美元，並需支付6000萬美元稅款。若最終無人領獎，獎金將會根據彩票銷售情况退回各州。<br />\n<br />\n(USA Today/中新網)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190215/s00005/1550201108991/美120億「兆彩」頭獎無人領-兩月後作廢\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190215%2Fs00005%2F1550201108991%2F%E7%BE%8E120%E5%84%84%E3%80%8C%E5%85%86%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%8D%E9%A0%AD%E7%8D%8E%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%98-%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%8C%E4%BD%9C%E5%BB%A2&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=0e5e5e0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190215%2Fs00005%2F1550201108991%2F%E7%BE%8E120%E5%84%84%E3%80%8C%E5%85%86%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%8D%E9%A0%AD%E7%8D%8E%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%98-%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%8C%E4%BD%9C%E5%BB%A2&h=0b88657e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190215/s00005/1550201108991/美120億「兆彩」頭獎無人領-兩月後作廢</a>"},{"pid":"dfa374826069287e3ec6f9c4548fe2808c762188","tid":1022675,"uid":91604,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"得獎者個老公俾人炒左,而家返左香港住劏房,<br />\n唔知道自己中左獎<br />\n如果香港新聞有報導,應該好快有人會領獎"},{"pid":"8d94122d90cb7deaf5be6a88a11efc594efb07cc","tid":1022675,"uid":7359